//  Generated for banking simulator — all data is fictional
//  Coverage:
//    - 12 customers (8 individual, 4 corporate) across 3 branches / 2 countries
//    - 22 accounts (savings, current, fixed deposit, corporate)
//    - 6 bank staff users
//    - ~40 transactions with matching counterparties
