//   CA2001 = Corporate Current
//   FD2001 = Fixed Deposit Corporate
//
// Customer categories:
//   RETAIL   = standard retail
//   PREMIUM  = high-net-worth individual
//   CORP     = corporate / legal entity
//   SME      = small & medium enterprise
//
// Risk levels:
//   LOW / MEDIUM / HIGH
//
// Exchange rates (approximate, 2025):
//   1 USD = 2 500 CDF
//   1 EUR = 2 900 CDF
// ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

